## Guidelines

- Do not request rulings on hypothetical or non-customs issues.
- Avoid compound questions; one issue per question.
- Ensure factual assertions are fully supported by exhibits.
- Mark any uncertain legal citations with `[VERIFY]`.
- Note pending litigation, protests, or audits that could bar consideration.
- Use Bluebook format for all legal authorities.
